des:
The Tahoe Snow Skill provides daily snowfall and total snow depth for Tahoe-area ski and snowboard resorts.

Enable the skill to get started: say “Alexa, ask Tahoe Snow …” Use the skill to check snow conditions for 45+ resorts.
